direction right
styleMode shadow
colorMode pastel
typeface clean

title Rhizome — Basis (V1) Architecture

Team [icon: users, label: "Team / User"]

Local Machine [icon: server, label: "Local Machine — AMD Strix Halo · 91GB unified · ROCm", color: blue] {

  Sources [icon: folder, label: "Sources — docs, chats, PDFs, code"]

  Ingest Layer [icon: python, label: "Ingest (forked LLM-Wiki)", color: gray] {
    Ingest [icon: terminal, label: "ingest · dedup · merge"]
    Manifest [icon: file, label: "manifest + delta (content-hash)"]
  }

  Vault [icon: database, label: "VAULT — markdown + YAML (the contract)", color: green] {
    Pages [icon: document, label: "pages · wikilinks · primitive lifecycle"]
    Retrieval [icon: search, label: "index / summary (retrieval ladder)"]
  }

  Engine [icon: pytorch, label: "Model Engine (our build)", color: orange] {
    Synth [icon: python, label: "RAFT synth — Q + golden + 4 distractors + CoT-cited A"]
    Trainer [icon: gcp-cloud-gpu, label: "bf16 LoRA fine-tune (PEFT · ROCm)"]
    Gate [icon: grafana, label: "eval gate — keep-or-revert (autoresearch idea)"]
  }

  Trigger [icon: terminal, label: "trigger — user idle + vault changed", color: red]

  Model [icon: pytorch, label: "Local model — Qwen3 + RAFT adapter", color: purple]

  Serving [icon: server, label: "Serve — RAG retrieval → model"]
}

// knowledge in
Team > Sources: add knowledge
Sources > Ingest: distill
Ingest > Manifest: track delta
Ingest > Pages: write / update
Pages > Retrieval: keep current

// train-while-you're-away loop
Trigger --> Synth: when user leaves + delta exists
Retrieval > Synth: chunks (golden + distractors)
Synth > Trainer: training pairs
Trainer > Gate: new adapter
Gate > Model: promote if it beats current
Gate --> Trainer: else revert

// serving (grounded RAG)
Team > Serving: query
Retrieval > Serving: top-k chunks
Serving > Model: prompt + context
Model > Serving: grounded + cited answer
Serving > Team: answer
